metadata.name: MEMETOV NUTAIL ☲ Whalesink
metadata.description:
It's time to ready up lads. The Merge is upon us. 

Grab a Memetov Nutail for your memetic arsenal and to ensure KEK WIN$ in the fight against the Institutions! 

WEAP❒NS DISCLOSURE: The Memetov Nutail is manufactured by Whalesink Industries in a smowl secluded cabin in the [redacted] region of Appalachia. Using a proprietary family recipe, handed down for over 7 generations, the main ingredient is one of the hardest materials to seize on Earth. 

There is one grower on the planet and no one knows their name or location but the material is found in many household memes. The anon grower and shower, goes by Skifeham. The ingredient they are renowned for is called 'My Left Nut.' 

To this day, Whalesink Industries purports that their Memetov Nutail wouldn't be possible without that nut.  

No Nut, No Meme. Memetov or Bust™
